txt.en: Following the defeat of the Warden of Dol Guldur's dungeons, you were able to recover many treasures taken from the prisoners there.
The Dungeons of Dol Guldur are rumoured to be impregnable...but it is said that Gandalf the Grey twice entered that terrible place and escaped to tell of it.
Rescue at least seven of the prisoners at once
Defeat the Warden after freeing all of the prisoners in the Dungeons of Dol Guldur
More than seven prisoners rescued at once
